M|references|- With that covered, let's turn to...
M|references|- Now that you understand X, here's Y.
M|references|- That brings us to...
M|references|- Also,...
M|references|- Plus,...
M|references|- On top of that,...
M|references|- What's more,...
M|references|- Another benefit is...
M|references|- Beyond that,...
M|references|- In addition,...
M|references|- There's also...
M|references|**Note:** Use "moreover" and "furthermore" sparingly. They can sound AI-generated when overused.
M|references|- However,...
M|references|- But,...
M|references|- That said,...
M|references|- On the flip side,...
M|references|- In contrast,...
M|references|- Unlike X, Y...
